      "text": "ああ、{user}さん\nちょっと聞きたいことがあるんですけど、いいですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ {user} san\nThere's something I want to ask you‚ is that okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "は、はい。なんでしょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-yes. What is it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "さっき、そこの角で、すずとすれ違ったんですけど\n一人で歌ってて、ぶつかっても気付きもしませんでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Earlier‚ when I passed by that corner‚ I saw Suzu there‚ and\nshe was singing alone and didn't even notice when we bumped into each other",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "かと思えば、昨日、琴乃を見かけた時は\nなんか暗い感じで俯いたまま歩いてましたし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But yesterday‚ when I saw Kotono‚\nshe seemed gloomy‚ walking with her head down",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 24.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "生え抜きの子達が揃って様子が変なんです\nここの事務所、何かあったんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They all seem to be acting strange\nDid something happen in the office?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 31.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "今度、NEXT VENUSグランプリの\n歴代優勝者を集めた祭典に出ることになりまして",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We're going to participate in the NEXT VENUS Grand Prix\nwith gathering past winners",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "月ストとサニピで、麻奈の曲をカバーするので\nみんな気合いが入ったり、思うところがあったりで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We're covering Mana's song with Moon Tempest and Sunny Peace‚ so\neveryone's feeling pumped up or have their own thoughts…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.7333356221,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.2333356221
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈……ああ、長瀬麻奈\n確かmihoが執念燃やしてた、あの人ですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mana… Ah‚ Mana Nagase\nThat person miho was so obsessed with‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.6333356221,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.4666689555
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_01-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "で、今度はみんなで彼女の曲をカバーする、と\n私よく知らないんですけど、そんなに凄かったんですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So now everyone's covering her song together\nI don't know much about it‚ was she that amazing?",
        "id": ""
      },
